'''派屈克·休斯'''（{{lang-en|Patrick Hughes}}，{{bd|1978年|}}）是一位[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]男導演，較知名的作品如群星动作片《[[敢死队3|敢死队3]]》（2014年）和動作喜劇片《[[殺手保鑣|殺手保鑣]]》（2017年）。

==生平==
休斯曾在电影学院学习三年，在年轻时开始执导了一些短片。<ref name="filmmakermagazine">{{cite web|title=A Talk with ''Red Hill'' Director Patrick Hughes|url=http://filmmakermagazine.com/15814-a-talk-with-red-hills-patrick-hughes/|accessdate=2010-11-04|publisher=filmmakermagazine.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418183324/https://filmmakermagazine.com/15814-a-talk-with-red-hills-patrick-hughes/|archive-date=2021-04-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年执导了首部长片《[[月正當中|月正當中]]》。休斯原會執導好萊塢版的《[[全面突襲|全面突襲]]》<ref name="screenrant">{{cite web|title='Expendables 3' Director Confirmed to Helm 'The Raid: Redemption' Remake|url=http://screenrant.com/raid-redemption-remake-expendables-3-director/|accessdate=2014-03-30|publisher=screenrant.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190206074718/https://screenrant.com/raid-redemption-remake-expendables-3-director/|archive-date=2019-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但後傳出他放棄執導的消息。

2017年，他執導了動作喜劇電影《[[殺手保鑣|殺手保鑣]]》<ref name="Mar2016TW">{{cite news|last1=Verhoeven|first1=Beatrice|title=Ryan Reynolds' 'Hitman's Bodyguard' Lands Director Patrick Hughes|url=http://www.thewrap.com/ryan-reynolds-hitmans-bodyguard-lands-expendables-3-director-patrick-hughes/|accessdate=2016-04-10|work=TheWrap|date=2016-03-09|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163209/https://www.thewrap.com/ryan-reynolds-hitmans-bodyguard-lands-expendables-3-director-patrick-hughes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

